{
  "chapter": 43,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十三回 门里门外\n\n阳光和小方在树林中遇到班察巴那，得知卜鹰仍然活着。班察巴那展现出高超的隐藏能力，在大树根部的地洞中藏身。他要求阳光和小方脱下衣服和鞋子，并将小方的剑交给他，用以制造二人已死的假象。班察巴那找到一具替死尸体，穿上小方的衣服，拿着小方的剑，从危崖上推下，让敌人相信小方和阳光已经摔死。\n\n班察巴那用光阴树的汁液涂抹二人面部，使其皮肤变黑起皱，看起来老了十岁，以此改变面貌。他安排二人伪装成一对贫穷的藏汉夫妻，以做生意为名加入商队，前往虎口集合，找到联络人大烟袋，再由其引荐给商队领队花不拉。班察巴那为二人编造了美雅和苗昌的假名，嘱咐他们在一年之内找到卜鹰。小方和阳光对班察巴那的周密安排深感佩服，彼此间的信任也在危难中更加深厚。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "班察巴那！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才出手的人是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜鹰呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有看见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也正在找他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道他在哪里吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我知道他绝对没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为那些人也在找他，可见他们也知道他还没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论谁要卜鹰的命都很不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果有人想要你的命，恐怕更不容易。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们都以为你已经逃出了树林，想不到你却在这棵树底下。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪卜鹰常说，如果你想躲起来，天下绝没有任何人能找得到你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也知道你还想说什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还想说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说我是条老狐狸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不是老狐狸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两百条老狐狸加起来也比不上你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们快躲进去。这个洞绝对可以容纳下你们两个人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们用不着替我担心。我有法子对付他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是你们一定要等我回来之后才能出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还要你们做一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "把你们的衣服和鞋子都脱下来给我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样够不够？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过你还得把你的剑交给我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你信任我，你是我的朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我绝不会让你失望的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我喜欢笑，常常笑，可是你以前好像从来也没有问过我在笑什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你为什么要问？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为……因为我要提醒你一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是个男人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你是个男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天下所有的男人都差不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你如果再笑一笑，我就……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就怎么样？是不是想打我的屁股？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你果然是卜鹰的好朋友。卜鹰果然没有看错你。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜你已经死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已经死了？什么时候死的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么死的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从一个危崖上摔了下去，摔死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的头颅虽然已经像南瓜般摔碎，可是别人一定还能认得出你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你身上还穿着他们看见过你在穿的衣服，手里还拿着你的剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果你没有死，当然绝不肯将那么样一柄好剑交给别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当然也死了。你们两个人全都死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们为什么要死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许你们是为了卜鹰，也许你们是失足落下去的。每个人都有很多种原因要死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说不定还有人会认为你们是为了怕私情被卜鹰发现，所以才自杀殉情的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道我为什么一定要你们死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我要你们去做一件事。一件绝不能让别人知道你们要去做的事，只有死人才不会被别人注意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？你要我们去做什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去找卜鹰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你们一定要报复，说不定现在就想去找卫天鹏，去找吕三。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是现在我们一定要忍耐。不管我们要做什么，都一定要等找到卜鹰再说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已知道这件事并不容易，但是只要我们有信心，也不是做不到的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的族人替这种树起了个很特别的名字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "光阴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "光阴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的族人都叫这种树为光阴树。因为光阴总是会使人变丑变老的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么掩护？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你已经不是蓝色的阳光，他也不是小方了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。这两个人现在都已经死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以现在你们已经是另外两个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是一对夫妻，很贫穷的夫妻，一定要奔波劳苦才能生存。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是做生意的，把藏边的特产运到关内去贩卖，挣一点蝇头微利。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你们没有父母子女，家里也没有别的人，也因为你们夫妻感情不错，所以你们不管到哪里去，总是两个人同行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们当然请不起镖师护送，为了行路安全，你们只有加入商队。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "商队？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "商队就是很多像你们这样的人结伴同行的队伍。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个商队并不大，大概有三四十个人。领导这个队伍的人叫'花不拉'，精明老练，对地形也极熟悉，少年时据说属于鞑靼的铁骑兵，曾经远征过突厥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们到哪里去才能找得到他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虎口。他们预定是在虎口集合的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们到了那里，先去找一个叫'大烟袋'的人，把你们的名字告诉他们，再付二十五两银子的路费给他，他自然会带你们去见花不拉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的名字叫什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是藏人，名字叫美雅。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的丈夫是汉人，名字叫做苗昌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我希望你们在一年之内找到卜鹰。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    }
  ],
